## Public Member Attributes

### Value0 {#accbdfd58f987c0f4687fb6785393e842}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>uint64&#95;t llvm::RangeListEntry::Value0</>}>
The values making up the range list entry.

Most represent a range with a start and end address or a start address and a length. Others are single value base addresses or end-of-list with no values. The unneeded values are semantically undefined, but initialized to 0.

Definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugrnglists-h/#l00035">35</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/debuginfo/include/llvm/debuginfo/dwarf/dwarfdebugrnglists-h">DWARFDebugRnglists.h</a>.
